wiki.content:
"Naturally" is a song performed by American band Selena Gomez & the Scene on their debut album, Kiss & Tell. It is written by Antonina Armato, Tim James, and Devrim Karaoglu. The song officially impacted U.S. mainstream radio on January 19, 2010. The song is an up-tempo electropop song in which the lead singer sings about a guy who is her perfect fit.
 
 "Naturally" is the band's highest charting song to date, charting as high as eighteen, which was in Canada, and also charting in the top thirty in the United States and New Zealand. It was their debut song to impact radio, and also the first to chart on the U.S Hot Dance Club Play chart
